OL,5, A tourist filmed carving names on to an
OL,6, inner wall at Rome's ancient Colosseum 
OL,7, says he did not realise how old the    
OL,8, monument was when he acted.            
OL,10,FUK-based Ivan Dimitrov made the comment
OL,11,Fin a letter of apology to Rome's mayor,
OL,12,Fsaying he understood "the seriousness  
OL,13,Fof the deed".                          
OL,15,FHe etched "Ivan + Hayley 23" - his and 
OL,16,Fhis girlfriend's names - on the        
OL,17,F2,000-year-old amphitheatre with a key.
OL,19,FHis actions in June were filmed by a   
OL,20,Fbystander and sparked condemnation.    
